		<div id="chatbox-header">
			<div><i class="fas fa-robot me-2"></i>JoeOne AI</div>
			<div class="close-chat"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></div>
		</div>
		<div id="chatbox-messages">
			<div class="message bot-message">Xin ch√†o! T√¥i l√† tr·ª£ l√Ω AI. T√¥i c√≥ th·ªÉ gi√∫p g√¨ cho b·∫°n h√¥m nay?</div>
		</div>
		<div id="chatbox-input">
			<input type="text" id="chat-input" placeholder="Nh·∫≠p tin nh·∫Øn c·ªßa b·∫°n..." />
